      <title>乌拉圭央行行长认为通胀目标仍有下调空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uruguay-central-bank-chief-sees-space-for-lower-inflation-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌拉圭央行行长华盛顿·里贝罗在接受采访时表示，乌拉圭下一届政府可能有空间降低年度消费者价格涨幅目标，因为货币政策控制着该国投资级同行中最快的通胀率之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uruguay-central-bank-chief-sees-space-for-lower-inflation-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:25:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
